    <section id="xio-drivers-addon-intro">
        <title>Introduction</title>
        <para>Here we describe a GPT bundle of some useful GlobusXIO drivers. The drivers are not
            packaged with the standard globus release because they require external dependencies, or
            are otherwise best distributed in a separate release. Here you can get each driver
            individually, or a bundle of all the drivers.</para>
